WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.870 --> 00:00:02.160
Good morning, family.

00:00:02.589 --> 00:00:08.189
I'm going to talk to you all about what's on my heart and what I've been praying about.

00:00:08.189 --> 00:00:12.893
You know the things I've seen whenever I pray.

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:19.670
People are asking me what I feel about what's going on with Israel and Iran right now.

00:00:20.120 --> 00:01:06.590
This is exactly what I tried to tell you all in March—it was probably the end of February—whenever the Lord told me that the month of April, during the eclipse, would be significant.

00:01:06.590 --> 00:01:46.840
I said nothing would happen during the eclipse, but after the eclipse, because of Passover, there would be an acceleration of war, weather events, financial issues, and signs in the heavens.

00:01:49.360 --> 00:02:18.255
The Lord told me back during Rosh Hashanah—and I'll repeat myself again—that from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, things would accelerate and almost double in the spirit realm.

00:02:18.255 --> 00:02:42.609
Then He came back to me and told me it would happen again during Passover and that things would accelerate even more.

00:02:57.800 --> 00:03:03.260
This was concerning red heifer things that were going to escalate because of this.

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:15.760
Here we are; it's happening right before our faces.

00:03:26.280 --> 00:03:31.509
All this stuff is happening on the news, and it's a big deal.

00:03:37.180 --> 00:03:56.653
I was interceding for it, and I told you all about the chemicals and the 50-gallon drums.

00:03:56.653 --> 00:04:09.819
It's very serious, what I saw coming out of Iran.

00:04:09.819 --> 00:04:33.720
Back when I started interceding for this, nothing was in the news about Iran wanting to do anything.

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:45.030
Now they're saying they're at war.

00:04:45.030 --> 00:05:07.820
Iran is saying they're not going to do anything more, but they're liars; they're planning something.

00:05:07.820 --> 00:05:21.800
This is where I was in intercessory prayer concerning this.

00:05:26.888 --> 00:05:49.240
I saw 50-gallon drums of biological weapons coming into Syria, traveling on the border of Iraq.

00:06:00.060 --> 00:06:01.697
I watched the truck in the spirit realm.

00:06:01.697 --> 00:06:14.000
As I said, this thing is just like a powderkeg.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:29.813
It's going to get even more intense.

00:06:39.630 --> 00:06:43.200
I don't know exactly when, but we haven't seen anything yet.

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:50.776
The Lord will protect His people.

00:06:55.809 --> 00:07:03.870
I believe with all my heart that we must intercede.

00:07:03.870 --> 00:07:16.600
There is a lot I've seen in the last 48 hours.

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:42.066
I went to a prayer meeting that Pastor Steve was having early in the morning.

00:07:42.066 --> 00:07:57.679
He invited me, and I started praying as a leader.

00:07:57.679 --> 00:08:36.100
Suddenly—and this usually doesn't happen in groups, I'm usually in the privacy of my home—the Lord started taking me into visions of things that were coming.

00:08:37.880 --> 00:08:53.138
The Lord warned me in that prayer meeting of attacks on American mega-churches.

00:08:57.584 --> 00:09:35.777
I saw an attack on a church in Florida and another on a church in North Carolina or South Carolina; I don't know exactly which state this man's church is in.

00:09:35.777 --> 00:10:01.436
I'm not going to name any names because this is a public platform, but it's a mega-church.

00:10:01.436 --> 00:10:23.869
Then the Lord said it's not only non-denominational; I saw Baptist, Catholic, and Methodist churches being attacked.

00:10:26.050 --> 00:10:50.566
It was a terrorist event related to ISIS that was going to try to take place on Sundays at American churches.

00:10:50.566 --> 00:11:16.440
I don't know exactly when, but it would be strategic, involving cells that crossed the border.

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:28.955
I saw attacks with explosives.

00:11:28.955 --> 00:11:39.220
Then I was shown professional Major League Baseball stadiums.

00:11:39.220 --> 00:12:11.925
They were trying to fly in drones—not huge military drones, but ones you could buy on Amazon—equipped with C4 to take out large crowds.

00:12:11.925 --> 00:12:36.259
They were using remote controls to fly into the stadiums and detonate them.

00:12:36.259 --> 00:12:50.907
I saw that in the vision—planned, strategic attacks in America.

00:12:50.907 --> 00:13:27.360
Then the Lord showed me an attack on Sydney Harbor at the big Opera House and warned me about something that was going to try to take place there.

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:40.771
I interceded for that at Pastor Steve's meeting.

00:13:40.771 --> 00:13:49.279
I saw some kind of escalation.

00:14:04.400 --> 00:14:35.560
What I was getting in the spirit was that there was a previous major event where people were hurt or passed away, but it didn't get enough national attention or create enough fear.

00:14:35.560 --> 00:15:16.195
Terrorist organizations in Australia were still plotting to take out a major landmark of significance to show they're the bullies and want everyone to fear them.

00:15:16.195 --> 00:15:43.326
Then I was shown the Olympics, and the Lord warned me to pray for them.

00:15:43.326 --> 00:16:12.470
If you live in Paris, I've told you before I saw fires and buildings on fire.

00:16:27.334 --> 00:16:29.143
I saw an attack against Paris and the Eiffel Tower with smoke coming up.

00:16:30.955 --> 00:16:43.309
I felt it was related to terrorist issues.

00:16:58.853 --> 00:16:59.119
I saw the President, Emmanuel Macron.

00:17:07.472 --> 00:17:10.173
I saw an attack on the aquatic centers during the Olympics.

00:17:10.173 --> 00:17:34.030
Pray for protection over the ceremonies and that all hidden things be revealed so there is no loss of life.

00:17:34.240 --> 00:17:42.760
I was bouncing all over the globe.

00:17:50.107 --> 00:17:54.450
The Lord was warning me about strategic things that terrorists were plotting.

00:17:58.012 --> 00:18:09.910
I saw a passenger train coming from Germany going into other parts of Europe.

00:18:19.937 --> 00:18:29.470
This train looked green, and it had explosives on it.

00:18:29.470 --> 00:18:41.020
These are the key things I saw in prayer.

00:18:41.020 --> 00:18:57.312
As an American, the visions of the churches and stadiums are serious.

00:18:57.312 --> 00:19:22.857
People should be watchful, not in fear, but aware of their surroundings even in church.

00:19:22.857 --> 00:19:26.119
Pray and obey.

00:19:26.119 --> 00:19:33.657
Plead the blood over your congregation.

00:19:33.657 --> 00:19:49.404
We have authority over those demonic spirits inside those terrorists.

00:19:49.404 --> 00:20:13.817
Bind the maneuvering of that devil and declare that no weapon formed against you shall prosper.

00:20:13.817 --> 00:20:20.907
We are in a very serious timeframe.

00:20:26.629 --> 00:20:30.567
Jesus Christ is coming, and the devil knows it.

00:20:31.964 --> 00:20:50.589
He sees what's going on in the spirit realm and knows his time is coming to an end.

00:20:50.589 --> 00:21:11.000
There will be a day when he is thrown into the Lake of Fire for all eternity.

00:21:13.730 --> 00:21:23.387
The season of Grace is coming to an end.

00:21:23.387 --> 00:21:37.360
We're getting ready for the Rapture and the seven years of tribulation.

00:21:37.360 --> 00:21:54.546
The devil is trying to bring forth the Antichrist agenda as quickly as he can.

00:21:54.546 --> 00:22:12.883
He has no power until the church is removed—until the Great Restrainer, the Holy Spirit who dwells inside us, is gone.

00:22:12.883 --> 00:22:20.900
We have the power to restrain the devil.

00:22:20.900 --> 00:22:34.846
This affects all Christians—Baptist, Methodist, Catholic, the whole Body of Christ.

00:22:34.846 --> 00:22:49.748
We all still love Jesus even if we don't agree on doctrine.

00:22:52.852 --> 00:23:00.935
I also warned you about Israel attacking Iran.

00:23:01.431 --> 00:23:16.960
I said many times that oil would go to $200 a barrel overnight because Israel retaliates.

00:23:18.062 --> 00:23:24.022
I saw refineries being attacked by the Israeli government.

00:23:24.022 --> 00:23:42.291
Now that Iran has acted, are we about to see Israel strike those oil plants?

00:23:42.291 --> 00:24:00.408
Oil shot up like a rocket, and gas was over $8 a gallon nationwide on average.

00:24:02.860 --> 00:24:09.413
I had this vision two years ago.

00:24:09.413 --> 00:24:20.960
Last year, the Lord warned me to pray over Coachella.

00:24:20.960 --> 00:24:39.679
I've sat on things for five years before they appeared in the news.

00:24:47.879 --> 00:24:48.680
I'm still praying over the situation in Italy.

00:24:51.141 --> 00:25:04.964
A major volcano is going to go off and wipe out a coastal city.

00:25:08.899 --> 00:25:11.142
I saw over 300,000 people dead.

00:25:11.142 --> 00:25:26.440
If you feel earthquakes or see smoke, get out because you don't have much time.

00:25:27.684 --> 00:25:32.719
I saw a huge tsunami wave.

00:25:32.719 --> 00:26:03.430
When Israel retaliates, there will be a lot of anti-Semitism because they caused the price of gas to go up.

00:26:03.430 --> 00:26:15.906
People will be rioting and protesting against the Jewish people.

00:26:15.906 --> 00:26:49.320
Regarding the major storm on the East Coast, I saw it move from New York all the way down past North Carolina and inland to Tennessee.

00:26:58.870 --> 00:27:03.114
It was a black haze over the land, linked to terrorist thinking.

00:27:03.114 --> 00:27:18.432
Big things are happening, and Jesus is coming soon.

00:27:18.764 --> 00:27:31.194
I believe 2025 is a year you should be watching.

00:27:32.840 --> 00:27:40.132
I personally believe New York is Mystery Babylon.

00:27:40.132 --> 00:27:53.377
Robert Breaker has a brilliant sermon on this.

00:27:53.377 --> 00:28:06.395
Our economy is about to crash in 2025.

00:28:06.395 --> 00:28:21.538
An angel visited me and told me to watch the mulberry bush.

00:28:21.538 --> 00:28:38.419
He told me the colors to watch and wrote on a copper pot.

00:28:45.506 --> 00:28:51.115
I saw the dinar going up in value.

00:28:51.115 --> 00:29:05.690
The dollar is going to go to 50 cents and crash.

00:29:05.690 --> 00:29:15.329
America will go through a Great Depression on steroids.

00:29:15.329 --> 00:29:44.180
There is a small window for the wealth of the sinner to be laid up for the just.

00:29:44.180 --> 00:29:57.159
This transfer is for the Remnant that is listening.

00:29:57.159 --> 00:30:07.651
Seek the Lord for relationship, not for money.

00:30:07.651 --> 00:30:21.773
If you have intimacy with Him, He will show you secret things.

00:30:21.773 --> 00:30:26.943
Let Him order your steps.

00:30:26.943 --> 00:30:45.480
Timing can vary, but I am confident these things will come to pass.

00:30:45.480 --> 00:30:50.480
Let's pray for peace.

00:30:50.480 --> 00:31:07.360
Father, I thank You for Your protection over everyone on this channel.

00:31:07.360 --> 00:31:14.526
Protect Israel and give Netanyahu supernatural wisdom.

00:31:25.675 --> 00:31:31.620
We call for a hedge of protection around the soldiers and the land.

00:31:35.982 --> 00:31:42.573
We plead the blood of Jesus over our churches.

00:31:46.342 --> 00:31:55.034
We pray for the FBI, CIA, and Homeland Security.

00:31:55.034 --> 00:32:04.960
Remove corrupt people and raise up righteous leadership.

00:32:04.960 --> 00:32:14.945
Protect our border patrol and law enforcement.

00:32:16.919 --> 00:32:24.720
The shaking is coming, but the Remnant is ready to share the love of God, heal the sick, and cast out devils.

00:32:27.431 --> 00:32:31.520
We give You all the glory.

00:32:42.550 --> 00:32:42.900
In Jesus' name, Amen.

00:32:42.900 --> 00:32:56.391
Please like, subscribe, and click the notification bell.

00:32:56.391 --> 00:33:05.799
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:33:05.799 --> 00:33:06.857
God bless you.
